OL,3,CCodebreaker veteran celebrates 100th
OL,4,Cbirthday with Guard of Honour
OL,6,FVideo report by Ann O'Connor
OL,8,FA D-Day veteran has received a Guard
OL,9,Fof Honour from the Royal British
OL,10,FLegion to mark his 100th birthday.
OL,12,FBernard Morgan, was the youngest RAF
OL,13,FSergeant to land in Normandy on D-Day
OL,14,Fat just 20-years-old, and turned 100
OL,15,Fon Wednesday 7 February.
OL,17,F"I'm very pleased to reach this age,
OL,18,Fbut I am very fortunate that I'm not
OL,19,Fwaiting or any operation, all I've got
OL,20,Fis arthritis. I'm very very lucky,"
OL,21,Fsaid Mr Morgan.
