OL,6,F"They've put a lot of work into
OL,7,Fgetting this day going."
OL,9,FMr Morgan, now a Royal British Legion
OL,10,F(RBL) Ambassador, was born in
OL,11,FLongsight, , but now lives in in
OL,12,FCheshire.
OL,14,FHe regularly speaks to schools and
OL,15,Fcolleges about his experiences during
OL,16,FWorld War Two.
