OL,6,F"He's keeping it alive, he's keeping
OL,7,Fthese sacrifices by these young men,
OL,8,Fhe's keeping these stories alive.
OL,10,F"They'll never be forgotten when
OL,11,FBernard's around."
OL,13,FThe veteran hopes to return to
OL,14,FNormandy with the to mark D-Day 80 in
OL,15,FJune 2024, and attend the
OL,16,Fcommemorations of the 80th anniversary
OL,17,Fof what happened in Normandy.
