OL,6,FWhen asked about being a hero, Mr
OL,7,FMorgan says the real heroes are the
OL,8,Fones "who gave their lives for the
OL,9,Ffreedom we enjoy today".
OL,11,FMr Morgan was a codebreaker during the
OL,12,Fwar, using equipment which was so
OL,13,Fsensitive it could not be be captured
OL,14,Fby the enemy.
OL,16,FHe landed on Gold Beach at 6.30pm on D-
OL,17,FDay, 6 June 1944.
