OL,6,F"The wireless operator you had on your
OL,7,Fwatch were the same on every watch,
OL,8,Fthey were youngsters just like me," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"They called me Sergeant Morgan, the
OL,12,Fairman's friend.
OL,14,F"They're all buried in Normandy
OL,15,Ftogether, and I was putting a cross
OL,16,Fdown at one of the graves.
