OL,6,FTwo days before VE Day, Mr Morgan
OL,7,Freceived a telex to say: "German war
OL,8,Fnow over, surrender effective sometime
OL,9,Ftomorrow".
OL,11,FOn 8 May it was confirmed that the war
OL,12,Fin Europe had ended, he celebrated
OL,13,Fwith his fellow soldiers.JMr Morgan
OL,14,Fstill has the original telex, which
OL,15,Fhas not given the document to any
OL,16,Fmuseums and even managed to keep it
OL,17,Fsecret for 50 years.JHe left the RAF
OL,18,Fin February 1947 having originally
OL,19,Fvolunteered on his 18th birthday in
OL,20,FFebruary 1942.
