OL,6,FAfter the war, he worked on the
OL,7,Frailways and at where he was a
OL,8,Fturnstile operator for 57 years.
OL,10,FHe went on to sell programmes at
OL,11,FGresty Road until the Covid pandemic,
OL,12,Fbut still has a season ticket for
OL,13,Flife.JMr Morgan was also a sportsman,
OL,14,Fand narrowly missed out on qualifying
OL,15,Ffor the 1,500m at the 1948 London
OL,16,FOlympics, losing to Bill Nankeville,
OL,17,FBobby Davro's dad.
OL,19,FAt his celebrations, Mr Morgan
OL,20,Fexpressed his gratitude.
