OL,6,F"I am so grateful to you," he said. "I
OL,7,Fappreciate the effort you've made and
OL,8,Fit's cheered me up no end. But
OL,9,Fwhenever I attend any event, I always
OL,10,Fthink of those sailors, soldiers
OL,11,Fairman, airwomen and the civilians who
OL,12,Fgave their lives for the freedom that
OL,13,Fwe enjoy today,.
OL,15,F"Regarding the way the home have
OL,16,Flooked after me, they've been most
OL,17,Fkind to me and set up all these
OL,18,Fdecorations and kept my in good
OL,19,Fhealth, I'm so grateful to the manager
OL,20,Fand all the staff."
