OL,6,FMr Morgan was joined by the Mayor of
OL,7,FEast Cheshire, representatives from
OL,8,Fthe Royal Air Force and the Chairman,
OL,9,FCharles Grant, and Manager, Lee Bell,
OL,10,Ffrom Crewe Alexandra to mark his
OL,11,Fspecial day.
OL,13,F"There is few survivors and Bernard is
OL,14,Fone of the special ones because of his
OL,15,Fmemories, he remembers everything,
OL,16,Fhe's a loving testament of the Kohima
OL,17,Fto the words that the British legion
OL,18,Fuse every meeting and every
OL,19,Fremembrance service," said Nancy Kay,
OL,20,FBranch Chair of for the Royal British
OL,21,FLegion in Crewe.
