OL,6,F"For those who don't know what the
OL,7,FKohima is, it starts with the words
OL,8,Fwhen you go home tell them of us and
OL,9,FBernard Morgan has been doing that for
OL,10,F50 years and is still doing it, and
OL,11,Fhe's just a marvellous man."
OL,13,FHis daughter, Sheila Borrington, also
OL,14,Fattended the event and said he is an
OL,15,Fode to his service and the family,
OL,17,FShe said: "It's absolutely wonderful
OL,18,Ffor him, it's so lovely to see so many
OL,19,Fpeople coming to celebrate with him.
