OL,6,F"He's such an inspiration to our
OL,7,Ffamily, to all of us but his war
OL,8,Fexperiences have had a profound effect
OL,9,Fon his life and we speak to several
OL,10,Fgroups and schools and dad always
OL,11,Fwants future generations to remember,
OL,12,Fbut reconciliation is important as
OL,13,Fwell to him.
OL,15,F"We cannot thank him enough for his
OL,16,Fservice, and the service of others at
OL,17,Fthat time."
